		<h3>Highlighted Restaurants</h3>
		<p>The highlight restaurant is a restaurant that has a uniqueness to itself and continues to push itself into the food scene either as
		an up and coming or a seasoned restaurant that deserves to be featured. We hope to allow less informed people of the multitude of food
		scenes that they can hopefully get to experience and decide for themselves if it is getting the recognition it deserves.</p>
		<table align="center">
			<tr>
				<td><h2>McDonalds</h2></td>
				<td><img src="assets/images/DayImg/McDonaldsRestaurant.jpg" 
				width="400" height="170"></td>
				<td>McDonald's is undoubtedly a standout in the fast-food culinary landscape, and we firmly believe it deserves recognition and 
				celebration for its extensive menu offerings and unwavering consistency. While McDonald's is a household name, it remains a 
				pioneer in the industry by continually introducing innovative menu items. Its wide range of choices caters to diverse tastes,
				making it an ideal choice for virtually anyone. Given these factors, we are proud to showcase McDonald's as a highlighted 
				establishment in the world of fast food.
				</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td><h2>Wendy's</h2></td>
				<td><img src = "assets/images/DayImg/WendysRestaurant.jpg"alt="Wendy's Restaurant" width="400" height="170"></td>
				<td>Wendy's stands as one of the prominent giants in the fast-food industry, emphasizing its robust and hearty menu offerings, 
				perfect for those seeking a more substantial meal. This renowned establishment reliably delivers satisfaction and never leaves
				patrons hungry. Thanks to Wendy's ability to consistently provide hearty and fulfilling options, we have chosen to feature it 
				among our highlighted restaurants.
				</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td><h2>Pizza Hut</h2></td>
				<td><img src="assets/images/DayImg/PizzaHutRestaurant.jpg"
				alt="Pizza Hut Restaurant" width="400" height="170"></td>
				<td>Pizza Hut stands out as a pizzeria that remains committed to the concept of family dining, diverging from the typical fast-food 
				approach. It steadfastly maintains its unique identity, setting itself apart from other similar establishments. Pizza Hut is the 
				natural choice for families seeking a dining experience that combines the pleasures of restaurant dining with the delectable taste 
				of pizza and a diverse range of accompanying dishes. For these compelling reasons, we highly recommend Pizza Hut, not only for its 
				delicious food but also for the enjoyable restaurant atmosphere it provides.
				</td>
			</tr>
